{"lemma":"ثُلْثَيْ","slug":"ثُلْثَيْ","root":"ثلث","root_slug":"ثلث","root_link":"/words/roots/ثلث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ثُلْث","root":"ثلث","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4618","n4619","n4620","n4621"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D8%AB%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"one third"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thuluth (an Arabic script style)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to triple (multiply by three)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do something three times, include three persons, etc."},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make triangular"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From ثلاث, from the root ث ل ث (ṯ l ṯ)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4618","headword_ar":"ثُلْثٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vuluvN","text_ar":"ثُلُثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4619","headword_ar":"ثِلْثٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"third young one"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, K,) of a she-camel, (M, K,) and, accord, to Th, of any female: (M:) and in like manner others are termed, to ten [inclusive]. (A.) But one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN vilovN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ ثِلْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[after the manner of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vinoYN","text_ar":"ثِنْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (M.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaY naxolahu Alv~ilova","text_ar":"سَقَى نَخْلَهُ الثِّلْثَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He watered his palm-trees once in three days:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he watered them"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda Alv~unoyaA","text_ar":"بَعْدَ الثُّنْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which app. means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after excepting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"omitting, one day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilovN","text_ar":"ثِلْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not used [thus] except in this case: there is no"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilov","text_ar":"ثِلْث"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the watering of camels; for the shortest period of watering is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rifoh","text_ar":"رِفْه"},{"kind":"text","text":"when the camels drink every day; then is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gib~","text_ar":"غِبّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is when they come to the water one day and not the next day; and next after this is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riboE","text_ar":"رِبْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; then, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximos","text_ar":"خِمْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so on to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei$or","text_ar":"عِشْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says As: (S, TA:) and this is correct, though J's assertion that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vilov","text_ar":"ثِلْث"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not used except in this case is said by F to require consideration. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aY Alv~ilovi","text_ar":"حُمَّى الثِّلْثِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~aY Algib~i","text_ar":"حُمَّى الغِبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tertian fever;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fever that attacks one day and intermits one day and attacks again on the third day;"},{"kind":"text","text":"called by the vulgar ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almuval~ivapu","text_ar":"المُثَلِّثَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["M","A","K","S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4620","headword_ar":"ثُلَثٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4621","headword_ar":"ثُلُثٌ","root":"vlv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulovN","text_ar":"ثُلْثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vulavN","text_ar":"ثُلَثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which last is either a dial. var. or is so pronounced to make the utterance more easy, (MF,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A third; a third part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valiytN","text_ar":"ثَلِيتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, T, S, M, Msb, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamiynN","text_ar":"ثَمِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabiyEN","text_ar":"سَبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sadiysN","text_ar":"سَدِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamiysN","text_ar":"خَمِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiyfN","text_ar":"نَصِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) though AZ ignored"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valiyvN","text_ar":"ثَلِيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S) and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":348},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamiysN","text_ar":"خَمِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivolaAvN","text_ar":"مِثْلَاثٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., app, signifies the same:] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlv","text_ar":"ثلث"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vlyv","text_ar":"ثليث"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (M,) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avolaAvN","text_ar":"اَثْلَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, Msb.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyapu $ibohi AlEamodi A^avolaAvFA","text_ar":"دِيَةُ شِبْهِ العَمْدِ اَثْلَاثًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The expiatory mulct for that"},{"kind":"text","text":"homicide"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which resembles what is intentional"},{"kind":"text","text":"shall be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thirds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e., thirty-three she-camels each such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiq~ap","text_ar":"حِقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and thirtythree of which each is such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ja*aEap","text_ar":"جَذَعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and thirty-four of which each is what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","A","Msb","K","MF","As"]}]}}